Gem Output Yet to Hit Pre-Crisis Levels, Allan Hochreiter Says

-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 
2011-06-29T08:49:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/gem-output-yet-to-hit-pre-crisis-levels-allan-hochreiter-says.html
World diamond production and prices
are still to reach levels seen before the financial crisis in
2008, said James Allan, founder of Allan Hochreiter Ltd., in a
speech today in Gaborone, the capital of  Botswana .  Allan Hochreiter , based in Johannesburg, advises on mineral
transactions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
